{"tid":2508352,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"黃竹坑站晉環收票旺挑戰今年票王 5日收逾4600認購登記","createTime":"2021-04-28T16:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T17:33:07.000Z","uid":4312,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8b07baf493ea666686bce5fbf823c1eb32d3a8f2","tid":2508352,"uid":4312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T16:15:35.000Z","msg":"港鐵黃竹坑站港島南岸第1期晉環繼續收票，截票時間為4月29日傍晚6時，目前晉環收票5日，暫收逾4600個認購登記，將挑戰新盤2021的票王。<br />\n<br />\n路勁地產銷售及市場推廣總監封海倫指晉環自公布第1號價單起，市場反應非常理想，截至今日4月28日下午7時正，短短5天已錄得逾4,600個認購登記，以首批240伙計算，超額逾18倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2944051/黃竹坑站晉環收票旺挑戰今年票王%205日收逾4600認購登記\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2944051%2F%E9%BB%83%E7%AB%B9%E5%9D%91%E7%AB%99%E6%99%89%E7%92%B0%E6%94%B6%E7%A5%A8%E6%97%BA%E6%8C%91%E6%88%B0%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E7%A5%A8%E7%8E%8B%25205%E6%97%A5%E6%94%B6%E9%80%BE4600%E8%AA%8D%E8%B3%BC%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzYGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=0497e599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2944051/黃竹坑站晉環收票旺挑戰今年票王%205日收逾4600認購登記</a>"},{"pid":"6b0ea9daa9e417d52c730fa30291708d95118468","tid":2508352,"uid":308028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T16:47:45.000Z","msg":"其實4600張係好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13253d1215b91977a2c3edf2d21711cd9432a58","tid":2508352,"uid":268,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6b0ea9daa9e417d52c730fa30291708d95118468","tid":2508352,"uid":308028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T16:47:45.000Z","msg":"其實4600張係好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"呢個價 4600張其實好多 <br />\n門檻根本同破萬票既盤唔同"},{"pid":"04d25cabdd5ba9c204195808317d40b506dd9237","tid":2508352,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:33:07.000Z","msg":"支持"}]}